    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 34.</p><p>Legendary Inspiration</p><p>Also at 20th level, you gain the ability to inspire legends. As a bonus action on your turn, you can expend 1 Legendary Point and a use of your Bardic Inspiration to inspire a creature within 120 feet. The creature regains 1 Legendary Point and becomes inspired as per your Bardic Inspiration feature.</p></div>",
